    <section class="bg-slate-700 py-20 relative">
      <h1 class="text-4xl pb-2 px-5">Who am I?</h1>
      <p class="pb-20 px-5">
        I am a 23 year old software engineer,
        I have a passion for technology that is driven by its capability to solve
        humanities issues and reduce the struggles of our society as a whole.
        As I return to work this is where I have decided to track my journey. I
        don't like social media so that method of sharing was dead in the water,
        and this presented a particular freedom i've been looking for when it
        comes to expressing myself online.
        I've been doing web development since I was around 10 years of age, at
        that time just tinkering with html,css and a bit of php. There's always
        been a beautiful sense of artistry to me when it comes to designing the
        user expreience that helps deliver a message or product. 
        I primarly spend time pondering problems looking to create solutions,
        when i'm not doing that i'm working in my home lab to better understand new and cutting edge tools to keep
        myself knowledgeable in the field or flying planes in Digital Combat Simulator.
      </p>
