        </svg>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-slate-600 py-24 relative">
      <h1 class="text-4xl pb-2 px-5">My Drive?</h1>
      <p class="px-5">
        I grew up in and around Flint, Michigan most of my life.
        Seeing the poverty and struggle that was present drove me
        to want to help those in need out of the cycle. 
        As I grew older my physical condition got worse. 
        At this time I saw a need for STEM education in the area
        as the sector is growing and the education could help bring back some social wealth to the city.
        I currently live in Grand Blanc, Michigan and I'm working to be able to provide that education through
        an open and free online resource.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section class="bg-slate-700 py-20 relative">
