      <h1 class="text-4xl pt-24 px-5">Why Here?</h1>
      <p class="pb-36 px-5">
        That's why after a bit of thought and consideration I settled on hosting
        my own blog. I not only intend to track my journey back into the Information
        Technology field but also post about what I am currently working on and
        occasionally journal on new technology I find interesting.
        I can't wait to look back one day on this page and have all the memories
        to enjoy. I hope you are excited to see this page evolve with me and
        join me in my journey.
      </p>
